{"tid":2414733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七國集團領導人視像會議　拜登料呼籲各國通力合作對抗中國","createTime":"2021-02-19T15:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T02:43:04.000Z","uid":350584,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"ff2cf91b01bc00d740e2117644ee69bdc2827c12","tid":2414733,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"拜登將透過視像，在慕尼黑安全會議發表外交政策講話，預料會提到中國和俄羅斯，帶來的經濟和國家安全挑戰，呼籲各國通力合作對抗中國政府，經濟上作弊和違反民主價值的政策和行為。拜登亦會表明，他並不尋求與中國對抗，或展開新冷戰，但預期並歡迎兩國有激烈競爭，強調民主而非獨裁，才能為世界帶來最好的前路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=424663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424663&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=efa676c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424663&h=d8458b10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=424663</a>"},{"pid":"dcbf346b88709923b5e58bb7a406b7fb22b7b0e3","tid":2414733,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】七國集團領導人舉行視像峰會，拜登首次以美國總統身份出席，他之後會在慕尼黑安全會議上，呼籲各國共同應對中國帶來的挑戰。"},{"pid":"ad77d63770c345530dc4f4ef28298b84c88a4de2","tid":2414733,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:48:23.000Z","msg":"係威脅"},{"pid":"e10e1140539cb7c6de617fec2e240a0e58f8f83d","tid":2414733,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呼籲各國通力合作對抗中國政府，經濟上作弊和違反民主價值的政策和行為。拜登亦會表明，他並不尋求與中國對抗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\